{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691780/extras/Steam_TheGame_Header.png?t=1685696584\" /><br><br><strong>Pixiescape is an asymmetrical multiplayer game, inspired by games like hide and seek or cops and robbers, where you play as a Fairy (hiding team) or a Robot (seeking team).</strong> <br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691780/extras/Fairy_Header.png?t=1685696584\" /><br>While playing as a fairy, the player will be able to build enchanted mushrooms (each with their own special effects), shoot magical orbs, or use their spells to evade getting captured. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691780/extras/GIF_1.gif?t=1685696584\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691780/extras/Fairy_MushroomOrb1.gif?t=1685696584\" /><br><br>Should the fairies get caught, they will be teleported to a jail where they can be rescued by remaining ally fairies. <br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691780/extras/Robot_header.png?t=1685696584\" /><br>While playing as a robot, the player's objective is to capture all fairies as quickly as possible. Robots can choose to equip skills from a completely different set of abilities such as a grapple hook, energy orbs that smash mushrooms, a scanner to detect hidden fairies, and many others.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691780/extras/Robot_SmashOrb1.gif?t=1685696584\" /><br><br>Once all fairies are captured, a 2nd round will begin where the players will switch roles. (Robots become fairies, fairies become robots)<br>The second team to play as fairies must outlast the first team's time to claim victory.<br><br>Team sizes can vary:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>1v1<br></li><li>2v2<br></li><li>3v3</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691780/extras/Steam_Features_Header.png?t=1685696584\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Both <strong>single-player</strong> and <strong>multiplayer</strong> modes are available (however, we strongly recommend playing with friends, as this tends to enhance the experience). You can also fill any remaining spots with AI.<br><br></li><li>Take advantage of our extensive <strong>customization options</strong> to create a unique look that suits you. All items are unlockable with the in-game currency acquired from playing.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691780/extras/Fairy_Customization.gif?t=1685696584\" />            <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691780/extras/Robot_Customization.gif?t=1685696584\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li>21 unique abilities between the two characters<br><br></li><li>6 diversified arenas to play on</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691780/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1685696584","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691780/page.bg.jpg?t=1685696584","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691780/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1685696584","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691780/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1685696584","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstat